Formal & Material Constraints


•  Formal Constraints 
–  Game elements that convey author’s  intended story 

•  Material Constraints 
–  Anything players are able  to control 

•  Agency & Immersion 
–  When players use material constraints  to produce 
story, optimally one that matches formal constraints 
–  Balance of formal & material  lead to  immersion and 
agency 

