Reasons for Shortcomings 

•  Unbalanced formal & material constraints

– Formal: renovate rundown  town 
– Material: move  in sims, build stuff 
– The extent of how you build stuff doesn’t

matter  to the game, only that you do  it.

– Agency  lost b/c material constraints don’t 
align with  formal constraints. 
– “Looks  like a danceclub, but doesn’t act  like 
one.” 

