Summary


•  The Sims 2 
– Able  to create and operate sims  in 
environments  that change dynamically with 
input 
– Formal and material constraints afford agency 
and allow  for  interactive experience 

•  MySims 
– Material constraints misaligned with  formal – 
game  is unresponsive  to user  input 
– Agency  is  lost 

